Lojban introductory lessons. Nick Nicholas (opoudjis@opoudjis.net).

These lessons are housed online at http://www.opoudjis.net/lojbanbrochure .
They are in Docbook XML. Consult http://www.opoudjis.net/lojbanbrochure/README.html
for instructions on set up, and 
http://www.opoudjis.net/lojbanbrochure/brochure.ann.html for details of the
content, and links to RTF, TeX (JadeTeX) and HTML versions of the text.

Lessons 1-8 and 10-11 were originally authored by Robin Turner. Lessons 9 and
12 onwards have been authored by Nick Nicholas, who has also revised the
remaining lessons.

